Test different ControlNet weights; higher weight increases the chances of obtaining a scannable QR code but also reduces the creativity of the AI.

<--- When the passthrough function is disabled, only the readable QR codes are saved. Unfortunately, the 'Read QR' node sometimes has an error where even scannable QR codes are not recognized. If you encounter too many errors, please manually check with your mobile device to confirm whether the codes are truly unscannable.
